    <header style="position:relative; top:14px;">
      <div style="background-color: #00375F;">
        <div class="container pt-5 pb-2">
          <div class="row featurette mb-3">
            <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
              <h1 class="featurette-heading fw-bold"  style="color: #FF8000;">Auditorio <span class="text-light fw-bold">TROX 360</span></h1>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main style="position:relative; top:14px;" id="#auditorio">
        <div class="album py-5">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row g-3 text-center">
              <div class="col-sm-12" style="position: relative; perspective: 1000px;">
                <img src="img/auditorio.jpg" width="100%" height="auto" style="border: none; padding: 0; border-radius: 15px;"/>
                <iframe id="iframe-vimeo" src="https://vimeo.com/event/886077/embed" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen 
                        style="position: absolute; top: 10%; left:10%; width:80%; height:80%; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); 
                                display: inline-block; text-align: center !important;">
                </iframe>
              </div>
              
              <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 text-center mt-2 mb-2">
                <a id="link-slidedown" class="link-chat-vimeo" href="javascript: void(0);"style="width:100%; display:inline-block;  padding: 15px 25px;">
                    Para acessar o chat, clique aqui!<br>
                    <span style="font-size: 15px;">Unete al chat! Pincha aquí.</span>
                </a>
                <div id="div-chat-vimeo" style="display:none; width:100%; height:auto; border:solid 3px #00375F; border-radius: 15px; padding: 0;">
                    <a id="link-slidedown" class="link-chat-vimeo" href="javascript: void(0);"style="width:100%; display:inline-block;">
                        Ocultar
                    </a>
                    <iframe id="iframe-interactio" src="https://vimeo.com/event/886077/chat/"
                    style="width:100%; height:400px; padding: 0; border-bottom-right-radius: 5px; border-bottom-left-radius: 5px;">
                    </iframe>
                    <a id="link-slidedown" class="link-chat-vimeo" href="javascript: void(0);"style="width:100%; display:inline-block;">
                        Ocultar
                    </a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 text-center mt-2 mb-2">
                <a id="link-slidedown" class="link-interactio" href="javascript: void(0);"style="width:100%; display:inline-block;  padding: 15px 25px;">
                    Precisa de tradução simultânea? Clique aqui.<br>
                    <span style="font-size: 15px;">Necesitas interpretación? Picha aquí.</span>
                </a>
                <div id="div-interactio" style="display:none; width:100%; height:auto; border:solid 3px #00375F; border-radius: 15px; padding: 0;">
                    <a id="link-slidedown" class="link-interactio" href="javascript: void(0);"style="width:100%; display:inline-block;">
                        Ocultar
                    </a>
                    <span id="texto-slidedown" class="" href="/lobby" style="width:100%; display:inline-block;">
                            1- Clique no centro do player. 
                        <br>2- Escolha a língua de sua preferência.
                        <br>3- Abaixe o volume da transmissão do Vimeo.
                        <br>4- Clique em ocultar.
                        <hr class="featurette-divider"><span style="font-size:12px;">1- Pincha en el centro del reproductor.
                        <br>2- Escoge el lenguaje de tu preferencia.
                        <br>3- Baja el volumen de la transmision de Vimeo.
                        <br>4- Pincha en Ocultar.</span> 
                    </span>
                    <iframe id="iframe-interactio" src="https://app.interactio.io/Agenda/DirectedAgenda?eventId=46644"
                    style="width:100%; height:700px; padding: 0; border-bottom-right-radius: 5px; border-bottom-left-radius: 5px;">
                    </iframe>
                    <a id="link-slidedown" class="link-interactio" href="javascript: void(0);"style="width:100%; display:inline-block;">
                        Ocultar
                    </a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <br>
              <diV class="col-sm-12 text-center mt-2 mb-2">
                <a id="btn-volver" class="" href="/lobby" style="width:300px; display:inline-block;">Lobby</a>
              </diV>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!--<hr class="featurette-divider">-->
        </div>
        
    </main>


    <footer style="position:relative; top:14px; background-color: #00375F;" class="footer py-3">
        <div class="container">
          <span class="text-light">Evento TROX 360 15 de Abril</span>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        $(document).ready(function(){
            $( ".link-interactio" ).each(function(){
                $(this).click(function() {
                    $( "#div-interactio" ).slideToggle( "slow"); 
                });
            });

            $( ".link-chat-vimeo" ).each(function(){
                $(this).click(function() {
                    $( "#div-chat-vimeo" ).slideToggle( "slow"); 
                });
            });
        });
    </script>
  </body>
